title: MEZZATESTA MAURIZIO
text:
I did want a different item and it said it was in stock online but when I got there they said I was supposed to click the item twice or something and it wasn't actually in stock. That's ridiculous, not my fault at all but somehow I should have known to click twice lol.
ANYWAY, I was still happy when I left because I found an acceptable replacement but I did have to pay more.
